{
  "stem": "6777.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody, every Pole, or every person living on the Polish side-- because there have been the ethnic Germans, as well-- had to have it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had to front up in their office like you have here, electoral office, they have been offices.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to front up, and they've been issued.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to bring your birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you got issued with the card.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family-- everybody, including Vera's husband, first, Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Vera-- no, Vera didn't go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Vera was too frightened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But [INAUDIBLE] grandmother with two kids and I, we fronted up and got a false birth certificate, of course, presented it, and got the real identity cards issued by the Germans, which-- but in a new name, of course.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bogacka, which means in Polish the same as rich, translated, simply translated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was false ones from the resistance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that depends.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If somebody could pay for it, they asked for it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If absolutely impossible, if it was a very, very poor person-- he got it without.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "100 Zloty, 100, 150.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That if they have finally decided to leave the ghetto, if they had a  means or somebody who would help them, then they could go onto the Polish side and live in hiding.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For example, after the first-- or was it the second aktion?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The cashier of the Judenrat by the name of Melamed, he lost his wife.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, I thought for a minute I kicked you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He lost his wife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after he lost his wife, he has decided to leave the Judenrat and leave the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I've brought him a Kennkarte.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He contacted his friends from before the war in Praga, in the same suburb where we lived before the war.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
